code: @Override public String toString() {     final StringBuilder buildy = new StringBuilder().     buildy.append("Id: ").append(id).     buildy.append(", Name: ").append(name).     buildy.append(", Object: ").append(object).     buildy.append(", Description: ").append(description).     buildy.append(", SortOrder: ").append(sortOrder).     return buildy.toString(). }

code: /**  * Returns approvals for specific Salesforce object type.  *  * @param object  *            type  * @return approvals of specified type  */ public List<Info> approvalsFor(final String object) {     return approvals.getOrDefault(object, Collections.emptyList()). }
